txt.en:
'I didn't even get to be one of the popular bestowers, like one of the level up quest bestowers. Oh, and did you notice who the level 50 level up quest bestower is? Yep, Maid of Lions. There's hubris for you!

'There I go again, you probably don't care about the problems of a little-old reputation bestower, do you? Let me get to the matter at hand.

'If you want to be an \qAlly\q of the Algraig, speak to me again.'
'Alright, soon you will be an Ally of the Algraig. Ready?'
By completing this quest, you will be considered an Ally of the Algraig.
